subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
lead_paragraph: U.C. Irvine used the 7-foot-6 Mamadou Ndiaye and the 7-2 Ioannis Dimakopoulos to dominate the lane, and the lead was never larger than 5 points.
